WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.599 --> 00:00:01.710
High Crime Vatican City... and 7 other Amazing
Facts

00:00:01.710 --> 00:00:04.529
1.

00:00:04.529 --> 00:00:08.240
Wikipedia to date has taken about 100 million
man-hours to create.

00:00:08.240 --> 00:00:12.520
This may sound like a lot, but in fact in
a typical month, people in the U.S. alone

00:00:12.520 --> 00:00:16.770
spend about 1.5 billion man hours watching
advertisements on TV.

00:00:16.770 --> 00:00:17.770
(QF 473)

00:00:17.770 --> 00:00:18.770
2.

00:00:18.770 --> 00:00:21.980
Alaska is the Eastern, Western, and Northern
most state in the U.S..

00:00:21.980 --> 00:00:22.980
How?

00:00:22.980 --> 00:00:27.030
Some of the Aleutian islands that are part
of Alaska cross the 180 meridian line, which

00:00:27.030 --> 00:00:29.780
is the marker between “East” and “West”
(QF 441)

00:00:29.780 --> 00:00:30.780
3.

00:00:30.780 --> 00:00:34.980
The highest crime rate per capita of any city
in the world is at Vatican City where an average

00:00:34.980 --> 00:00:38.909
of 600 crimes are committed per year, despite
only having 800 residents.

00:00:38.909 --> 00:00:39.909
(QF 459)

00:00:39.909 --> 00:00:40.909
4.

00:00:40.909 --> 00:00:42.629
The Sun is 20 “years” old in Sun years.

00:00:42.629 --> 00:00:47.429
You see, it’s completed about 20 orbits
around our galaxy’s center since it first

00:00:47.429 --> 00:00:48.510
sparked to life.

00:00:48.510 --> 00:00:49.510
(QF 467)

00:00:49.510 --> 00:00:50.510
5.

00:00:50.510 --> 00:00:53.370
The Jews were not the only civilization to
mark a great flood that seemingly covered

00:00:53.370 --> 00:00:58.489
the Earth for a certain period (note: 40 days
and 40 nights was just a Jewish expression

00:00:58.489 --> 00:01:03.879
that meant "a really long time" and didn't
necessarily literally mean 40 days and 40

00:01:03.879 --> 00:01:04.879
nights).

00:01:04.879 --> 00:01:07.710
Here is a small subset of other cultures that
had similar stories:

00:01:07.710 --> 00:01:08.710
a.

00:01:08.710 --> 00:01:12.180
Ancient Greek literature states that "Zeus
sent a flood to destroy the men of the Bronze

00:01:12.180 --> 00:01:13.180
Age.

00:01:13.180 --> 00:01:16.890
Prometheus advised his son Deucalion to build
a chest after floating in the chest for nine

00:01:16.890 --> 00:01:19.320
days and nights, landed on Parnassus.

00:01:19.320 --> 00:01:22.710
When the rains ceased, he sacrificed to Zeus,
the God of Escape."

00:01:22.710 --> 00:01:23.710
b.

00:01:23.710 --> 00:01:28.149
Lithuanian legend states that water once covered
the Earth for a period of 20 days and 20 nights.

00:01:28.149 --> 00:01:32.741
Those few who survived were 9 couples, from
which the Lithuanian tribes originated, according

00:01:32.741 --> 00:01:33.960
to their legend.

00:01:33.960 --> 00:01:34.960
c.

00:01:34.960 --> 00:01:38.359
Burmese legend says that when the great flood
came, a brother and sister took refuge in

00:01:38.359 --> 00:01:39.359
a boat.

00:01:39.359 --> 00:01:43.240
The sister later gave birth, but a witch cut
the baby into pieces; the pieces of the baby

00:01:43.240 --> 00:01:48.119
struck the ground and the nations of the Earth
sprung up from the slain child's body parts.

00:01:48.119 --> 00:01:49.119
d.

00:01:49.119 --> 00:01:53.259
Transylvanian legend says a certain man announced
the coming of a cataclysmic flood.

00:01:53.259 --> 00:01:56.930
According to their legend, the predicted flood
lasted an entire year.

00:01:56.930 --> 00:02:01.979
e. Sacramento Indian legend states that a
great flood once covered the Earth that lasted

00:02:01.979 --> 00:02:03.500
"9 sleeps".

00:02:03.500 --> 00:02:04.500
f.

00:02:04.500 --> 00:02:08.319
According to Chinese legend, the Earth was
covered in a great flood and only 2 children

00:02:08.319 --> 00:02:12.100
survived in a gourd; the period of the flood
was 99 days.

00:02:12.100 --> 00:02:16.630
From the two children came 12 offspring from
which the nations of the Earth arose.

00:02:16.630 --> 00:02:17.630
6.

00:02:17.630 --> 00:02:21.580
During WWII, all the snakes and dangerous
insects were killed in the London Zoo by the

00:02:21.580 --> 00:02:25.010
Zoo keepers in case they managed to escape
after a bombing.

00:02:25.010 --> 00:02:26.010
(QF 451)

00:02:26.010 --> 00:02:27.010
7.

00:02:27.010 --> 00:02:29.550
The 1900 Olympics included a long jump competition…
for horses.

00:02:29.550 --> 00:02:30.550
(QF 453)

00:02:30.550 --> 00:02:31.550
8.

00:02:31.550 --> 00:02:33.420
Oranges are a berry, as are bananas.

00:02:33.420 --> 00:02:41.360
Strawberries however are not technically berries,
they are aggregate fruits.

00:02:41.360 --> 00:02:50.510
(QF 458)

